{"tid":2518002,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國大紀元遭逐出美國國會記者團  採訪證遭吊銷 !","createTime":"2021-05-05T17:09:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T17:58:31.000Z","uid":219007,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f2806bbbddc98ef490c66a942d5002b8313d11df","tid":2518002,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T17:09:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3522361?fbclid=IwAR2LtPOM0LsN0n2CS8YHeaZ93jB-CAnbuimlF1FYJZActaVryasJNXEDDhY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3522361%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2LtPOM0LsN0n2CS8YHeaZ93jB-CAnbuimlF1FYJZActaVryasJNXEDDhY&d=lnSleIYCVJUMUgC9CFuHQugMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=3d9437b2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3522361%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2LtPOM0LsN0n2CS8YHeaZ93jB-CAnbuimlF1FYJZActaVryasJNXEDDhY&h=bfc390dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3522361?fbclid=IwAR2LtPOM0LsN0n2CS8YHeaZ93jB-CAnbuimlF1FYJZActaVryasJNXEDDhY</a><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國《福斯新聞》（Fox News）報導，知名反中共媒體《大紀元》證實遭逐出美國國會記者團，記者採訪證已遭吊銷，事件引發17名美國國會議員關切，但目前還不知道確切原因。<br />\n<br />\n美國《福斯新聞》主播卡爾森（Tucker Carlson）連線訪問美國《大紀元》主持人菲利普（Josh Philipp），菲利普表示，尚未收到國會的正式書面通知，媒體正在自力查明被逐出記者團的原因，但顯然國會允許中國官媒《新華社》、《人民日報》進入採訪，卻將《大紀元》拒於門外。<br />\n<br />\n菲利普表示，大眾新聞機構正試圖與中國加強聯繫，當中包括中共的統戰部門，或是與中國有商業利益往來的團體，而這似乎成了1種趨勢，有些新聞報導甚至有對價關係，而《大紀元》是對中共提出最嚴厲批評的媒體之一，長期關注中國異議人士和宗教信徒，「一直是中國共產黨的一針刺。」<br />\n<br />\n菲利普向卡爾森表示，「幸運的是，我們有17個國會議員前來捍衛我們（的採訪權），希望我們能盡快回到國會」，菲利普也坦言，後續狀況如何還要再看看。"},{"pid":"52336a0017c6784f66e180a5fbae25d4a2fb2d55","tid":2518002,"uid":366655,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T17:13:58.000Z","msg":"終於露底<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1b536b499cbe45c298783ed61da39f382f7f184","tid":2518002,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T17:51:30.000Z","msg":"兩黨共識，共產黨同民主黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b87f143d2ad636670e808a8a903f251e6d3d7467","tid":2518002,"uid":289257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T17:52:52.000Z","msg":"Fox News fake news<br />\n迫害我侵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bb7698516d93556a18575722e2f058b785e5610","tid":2518002,"uid":112846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T17:57:04.000Z","msg":"民主狗惡撚到仆街"},{"pid":"cf1e502e571dab4c204551af2dc9c39fcc9aca2c","tid":2518002,"uid":112846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T17:58:31.000Z","msg":"之前袁弓夷話想約民主狗議員傾下香港問題，班民主狗知佢見唔少共和黨人，就唔鬼覆佢既invitation<br />\n<br />\n民主狗就最撚小氣"}]}